This module contains the main loop for the Arturo VM.

Here:

  • we take a Translation (= constants + bytecode)
  • go through each and every one of the bytecode instructions and execute them, one by one

Imports

bytecode, errors, eval, globals, parse, profiler, stack, values/value, values/custom/vlogical
